  Te7 it chiuN 
  Bou2 sou2-chai7 u7 chit8-e5 lang5 siN3 Li2, sui-jian5 m7-si7 thak8-chheh bun5-nga2 e5 lang5, khiok iah8 ti-su sek-li2, lang5 long2 chheng-hou i kio3-cho3 Li2 sian-siN. I-e5 ke-lai7 sio2-khoa2 jiau5-ju7, u7 tam7-poh8-a2 chhan5-hng5 san2-giap8, in-ui7 bo5 kau3 thang eng7; sou2-i2 tiam3 goa7-bin7 cho3 seng-li2 than3 lai5 thiN-thiap. 
  U7 chhoa7 chit8-e5 bou2 siN3 Ho5, mng5-hong kap i saN-teng2-tui3, tui3 se3-han3 u7 hak8-sip8 bun5-ji7, seng3-cheng5 iu7-koh chhong-beng5. Che chiaN3-chiaN3 si7 ho2 in-ian5. TaN-chiah chhoa7 hit-si5 hu-chhe ho5-ho2 saN-thiaN3, hoan7 su7 saN-pang-chan7 teh liau7-li2, ia7 m7-sai2 hoan5-lo2 chiah8-chheng7. Au7-lai5 u7-siN nng7-e5 hau7-siN chit8-e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2. Gin2-na2 seng-seng5-put-siok8, pe7-bo2 khoaN3-kiN3 chin i3-ai3. In pe7 ti7 goa7-bin7 sou2 than3 e5 chiN5 theh8 to3--lai5 chiau3-kou3 ke-lai7 e5 lang5, long2 bo5 lam7-sam2 khai. In bou2 ti7 ke-lai7 tak8-jit8 cho3 lu2-kang lai5 thiN-thiap8 sou2-hui3. Chit8 ke e5 tiong-kan put-chi2 ho5-peng5 u7 chin e5 khoai3-lok8, bo5 liau7 Li2 sian-siN sim-lai7 bo5 pa2-chhi5, cho3 lang5 bo5 kian-teng7, m7-bat lang5 e5 gau5, gong7, ho2, phaiN2, lam7-sam2 chham lang5 kau-poe5, hou7 chit8-e5 phaiN2 e5 siau3-lian5-lang5 in2-iu2 khi3 kiaN5 bo5 cheng3-keng e5 lou7. Chhoa7-khi3 thit-tho5 keng, chiong jit8 chiong mi5 to si7 tiam3 ti7 hoa-ke-liu2-hang7, loan5-loan5 put-sia2, pou7-pou7 bo5 li7; iu7-koh kap lang5 io5-tau5 poah8-thoaN i2-kip8 pai5-a2 lian2-po2, hong3-kiam hou-kun5 kiat-tong2 lim-chiu2 chiah8 te5, sou2 u7 e5 chiN5-chai5 it-chin7 khai liau2-liau2. Chhu3-lai7 e5 bou2-kiaN2 pang3 bo5 iau3-kin2, bo5 beh chiau3-kou3, chiam7-chiam7 han2-tit to3--lai5, kau3-boe2 soa3 long2 bo5 kui-ke, in-ui7 hit-tiap8 bo5 chiN5-chai5 kap bo5 the2-bian7 e5 ian5-kou3, KiN3-tioh8 in bou2 chiu7 bo5 ho2-bin7 saN-khoaN3; kiN3-tioh8 in hau7-siN cha-bou2-kiaN2 bo5 thiaN3-thang3 e5 sim, tok8-tok8 phaiN2 khoan2-thai7 i. Au7-lai5 chiong i-e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 kap te7-ji7 hau7-siN beh chhoa7-khi3 be7-lang5, chiu7 chit-tiap8 i chit8-ke e5 kan-khou2 kau3-chia kek8-thau5 lah. 
  Te7 ji7 chiuN 
  U7 chit8-jit8 Li2 sian-siN ti7 bou2 siaN5 teh kiaN5 lou7 e5 tiong-kan, hut-jian5 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 keng e5 chhu3, koan5 koa3-toa7, khoan2-sit chham pat8-keng chhu3 bo5 siang7, koh khoaN3 che7-che7 lang5 tui3 hia teh chhut-jip8, m7 chai si7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3. I chiu7 toe3 cheng3 lang5 jip8-khi3, khoaN3-kiN3 thiaN-tng5 e5 lai7-bin7 cho2-iu7-peng5 pai5 kui2-na7 tsap8 liau5 e5 i2, che7-che7 lang5 ti7-hia teh che7 thiaN chit8 e5 bok8-su teh thoan5 to7-li2 kong2, ¡§U7 chit8 e5 chhong3-cho7 thiN-te7 ban7-mih8 e5 toa7 Chu2-chaiN2 e5 Siong7-te3, chiu7-si7 se3-kan lang5 e5 ThiN-pe7, put-lun7 sim2-mih8 kok, sim2-mih8 chok8, sim2-mih8 lang5, bo5 chit8 e5 m7 eng-kai keng3-pai3 hok8-sai7 I.¡¨ 
  Koh kong2,¡§Se3-siok8 sou2 pai3 e5 ngou2-siong7 i2-kip8 it-khai3 e5 sin5-beng5, ang-hut8 long2 si7 lang5 sou2 siat sou2 hong ke2 iaN3 e5 sin5, keng3 i, pai3 i, m7-na7 bo5 li7-ek, koh toa7-toa7 tek-choe7-tioh8 chin Chu2-chaiN2 e5 Siong7-te3.¡¨ 
  Iah8 teh kong2,¡§Lang5 long2 u7 choe7, sou2 kong2 sou2 kiaN5 sou2 siuN7 bo5 hap8 Siong7-te3 e5 hoat-tou7 kek8 che7. Sou2-i2 chai7-siN bo5 peng5-an, si2-liau2 ia7 tioh8 loh8 te7-gek8, siu7 heng5-hoat8 e5 po3-eng3.¡¨ 
  Iah8 teh kong2,¡§Lang5 be7 ka-ti7 siok8-hoe5 pun2-sin e5 choe7, ia7 bo5 hoat-tou7 thang hou7 ka-ti7 e5 sim toan-chiaN3. Na7 bo5 Siong7-te3 toa7-toa7 hian2-chhut I jin5-ai3, chu5-pi e5 sim lai5 kiu3 lang5, chiu7 lan2 lang5 long2 e7-si2, tiam3 ti7 choe7-ok e5 tiong-kan, bo5 chit8 lang5 e7 tit-tioh8 kiu3.¡¨ 
  Koh kong2,¡§Siong7-te3 ka7 thiN-e7 ban7-hng siat-lip8 chit8 e5 Kiu3-chu2, chiu7-si7 Ia5-sou lah; hoan7-na7 sin3-kho3 I e5 lang5 m7-na7 bian2-tit si2-au7 tim5-lun5 e5 kan-khou2, iah8 tek-khak thoat-li7 choe7-ok ti7 chit chai7-siN.¡¨ 
  Chhin-chhiuN7 chit ho7 e5 oe7, m7-na7 chit8 poaN3-ku3 nia7-nia7. Li2 sian-siN kin-a2-jit8 thiaN-kiN3--e5 sou2 boe7 bat thiaN-kiN3--e5, na7-si7 che7-che7 ku3-oe7 e5 tiong-kan tit-tioh8 chit8 ku3, kek8 po2-poe3 e5 oe7. Chit-e5 si7 sim2-mih8 leh? Chiu7-si7 Kiu3-chu2 e7 hou7 lang5 thoat-li7 choe7-ok ti7 chit chai7-siN. Li2 sian-siN sui-jian5 ham7-loh8 ti7 cheng3 choe7 e5 tiong-ng, sim-koaN ku2-ku2 be7 an-jian5. Kho2-sioh bo5 hoat-tou7 thang thoat-li7, chiu7 chit-e5 ke2 koe3-sit oaN7-sin e5 lou7, lian2 chhin-chhiuN7 teh-beh choat8-bang7. TaN hut-jian5 thiaN-kiN3 bok8-su e5 oe7, hoan2-hoe2 ke2-piN3 e5 sim chiam7-chiam7 oah8-tang--khi3-lai5, chong2--si7 boe7 chai che oe7 si7 khak-sit8 a2-bo5. Bok8-su ka3-si7 cheng3-lang5 liau2, chiu7 koh kong2, ¡§Hoan7-na7 u7 lai5 mng7 to7-li2--e5, chhiaN2 lin2 lai5-khi3 kheh-thiaN tam5-lun7 kui2-ku3 oe7.¡¨Li2 sian-siN thiaN-kiN3 sui5-si5 toe3 i khi3. I2-keng jip8 thiaN, bok8-su mng7 i kong2,¡§Sian-siN u7 beh mng7-khi2 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3?¡¨ In3 kong2, ¡§Tu2-a2 thiaN-kiN3 lo2-su sou2 kong2 Ia5-sou e7 kiu3 lang5 thoat-li7 choe7-ok, chin-chiaN3 u7 iaN2--bo5?¡¨ 
  Bok8-su kong2,¡§Che oe7 khiok-si7 chin-sit8.¡¨ 
  Li2 sian-siN mng7 kong2,¡§Ia5-sou e7 kiu3--goa2 bo5?¡¨ 
  Bok8-su kong2,¡§Sian-siN u7 sim2-mih8 choe7, beh ng3-bang7 kiu3?¡¨ 
  In3-kong2,¡§Se3-kan sou2 u7 e5 choe7 goa2 long2 hoan7-tioh8, chiau3 an2-ni sng3-si7 toa7 choe7 e5 lang5, m7 chai Ia5-sou e7 kiu3--goa2 bo5? ¡¨ 
  Bok8-su kong2,¡§Ia5-sou cho3 Kiu3-chu2 si7 bo5 sou2 be7-e7 kiu3. Sian-siN na7 chin-chiaN3 sin3 i, tek-khak tit-tioh8 kiu3.¡¨Bok8-su koh chiong sin3 Ia5-sou che7-che7 o3-biau7 e5 oe7 lai5 ka7 khui-thiah ka3-si7 i. Kong2-liau2 koh mng7 i kong2,¡§Sian-siN li2 u7 sin3 Chu2 Ia5-sou bo5?¡¨ 
  In3-kong2,¡§Sin3 ah! Ng3-bang7 Chu2 kiu3--goa2.¡¨ 
  Bok8-su kong2,¡§Lan2 nng7 lang5 tioh8 ki5-to2.¡¨ Chiu7 cho3-hoe2 kui7-loh8-khi3. 
  Bok8-su teh ki5-to2 e5 oe7 iok-liok8 chiu7-si7 kong2,¡§Khun2-kiu5 Kiu3-chu2 lin5-bin2 Li2 bou2 lang5, sia3-bian2 i-e5 choe7, kam2-hoa3 i-e5 sim. I hou7 mou5-kui2 pe2-pak8, tioh8 thau2-pang3 i. I u7 thian-liong5 e5 sim, tioh8 hou7 i siN oah8 hou7 i e7-tit chiaN5, cho3 oaN7-sin e5 lang5; ti7 se3-kan e7 cho3 seng3, chheng-khi3, bo5 la5-sam5; si2-au7 i-e5 leng5-hun5 e7-tit eng2-oan2 hiong2-hok ti7 Thian-tong5.¡¨ 
  Chiu7-si7 kong2 chiah-e5 oe7, ki5-to2 liau2, nng7 lang5 khi2-lai5, khoaN3 Li2 sian-siN e5 heng5-tong7-ki2-chi2, toa7-toa7 u7 siu7 Seng3-sin5 kam2-tong7. 
  Tui3 chit-tiap8 liau2-au7 sim chiu7 ke2-piN3 chiong5-cheng5 e5 chho3-gou7, siong5-siong5 ka-ti7 ki5-to2. I e5 tek-heng7 tak8-jit8 na2 oaN7-sin, bo5 loa7-ku2 jip8 Seng3-kau3 cho3 Chu2 e5 hak8-seng. 
  Au7--lai5 Li2 sian-siN hoaN-hi2 ka7 Ia5-sou cho3 kan-cheng3, na7 tu2-tioh8 lang5, chiu7 tek-khak kong2 chin e5 to7-li2 chin7 khui3-lat8 khou2-khng3 lang5, tioh8 sin3 Chu2 lai5 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Na7-si7 lang5 thiaN-liau2 gi5-ngai2, Li2 sian-siN tok8-tok8 ka7 i kong2,¡§Chu2 e7 kiu3 goa2 chit-ho7 toa7-choe7 e5 lang5, kiam2 be7 kiu3 lin2 mah?¡¨Lang5 thiaN i-e5 sou2 kong2, khoaN3 i sou2 kiaN5, tui3 an2-ni lai5 siu7 i kam2-hoa3--e5 be7 chio2. Iu7-koh chai7-cha2 i kau-poe5 hiah-e5 phiau5-tou2 e5 peng5-iu2, hit tong2-a2 e5 phaiN2 chu2-te7; chiong5-tiong ia7 u7-e5 ke2 koe3-sit, ka-ti7 oaN7-sin, kap i cho3-hoe2 lai5 kui-cheng3-kau3. U7 e5 bo5 sim2-mih8 beng5-pek8 chit-e5 to7-li2--e5, ia7 kiu5 i ka3-si7 in cho3 Chu2 e5 hak8-seng, mng7 i kong2,¡§Chit-e5 to7-li2 ki3-jian5 bo5 sim2-mih8 beng5-pek8, siaN2-su7 ai3 jip8 kau3?¡¨ In chiu7 in3 kong2,¡§Goan2 chiah-e5 sui-jian5 bo5 sim2-mih8 bat chit-e5 to7-li2, chong2-si7 long2 e7-hiau2 khoaN3 Li2 sian-siN piN3 phaiN2 cho3 ho2-e5, khi3-sia5-kui-cheng3, chiong hian7-kim siuN7-khi2 i chai7-cha2 toa7-toa7 bo5 sio siang7, na7 m7-si7 cheng3-to7 Li2 sian-siN an2-chaiN2-iuN7 e7 ke2-piN3 kau3 an2-ni-siN leh!¡¨ 
  Te7 saN chiuN 
  Li2 sian-siN jip8-kau3 liau2-au7 su7-su7 hou7 lang5 siau3-liam7 hang5-hok8, khai3 e7 kham-tit hou7 lang5 hang5-hok8--e5; chiu7-si7 i sit8-sim ai3 i ke-lai7 e5 lang5 tit-tioh8 hok-khi3. Chit8-piN chin7-sim cho3 seng-li2 lai5 iuN2-chhi7 choan5-ke, chit8-piN kong2 Seng3-keng hou7 ke-lai7 thiaN, eng7 che7-che7 e5 hong-hoat, che7-che7 e5 ke3-ti3 in2-chhoa7 i chhut sia5 e5 lou7, jip8 chiaN3 e5 lou7. 
  Li2 sian-siN jip8-kau3 liau2, chiu7 ai3 to3-lai5 ke-lai7, m7-ku2 chhiu2-thau5-an5 bo5 sou2-hui3, che7-che7 hang7 e5 boe7-pian7, tok8-tok8 tai7-seng kia3 chit8 tiuN phoe kap tam7-poh8 chiN5, chhiaN2 an-ui3 i ke-lai7 e5 lang5 nia7-tiaN7. 
  I e5 bou2 chiap-tioh8 phoe iah8 ki5-koai3, iah8 hoaN-hi2, teh kong2, ¡§Kin-a2-jit8 chit e5 tai7-chi3 si7 bang7-kiN3 a2-si7 chin-chiaN3, hou7 lang5 bo5 phah-sng3 kau3 an2-ni. Ko2-jian5 si7 goa2 tiong7-hu sou2 kia3 e5 phoe mah?¡¨KhoaN3 kui2-na7 pai2, koh kong2,¡§Si7 goa2 tiong7-hu chhin-chhiu2 sia2--e5 bo5 gi5 lah. Chong2--si7 chit tiuN phoe khoaN3--khi2-lai5, ho2-cheng5, ho2-i3, moa2-moa2 ti7 choa2-bin7, an2-chaiN2-iuN7 thai3 an2-ni? Kap chai7-cha2 toa7 koh-iuN7, chin-chiaN3 siuN7 be7 hiau2-tit, taN chong2--si7 theng3-hau7 i kui-ke chiah e7 chai.¡¨ 
  Au7-lai5, Li2 sian-siN chhiu2-thau5 khah iong7-leng7, u7 chhun chiN5, tek-i3 kui-ke. 
  Kau3 te3 chiu7 gu7-tioh8 i-e5 kiaN2, theng5-kha kap i kong2 kui2-ku3-oe7, hoaN-hi2 be7-kou3-tit, chiu7 saN-khan-chhiu2 jip8 chhu3-lai7. 
  I-e5 kiaN2 toa7-siaN kio3 i-e5 lau7-bo2 kong2,¡§Tia-ah! To3-lai5--lah. ¡¨ 
  In bou2 chau2 chhut--lai5, thiaN in ang e5 gian5-gi2 khoaN3 in ang e5 bin7-sek, put-chi2 un-jiu5 toan-chiaN3, ho5-peng5, pi2 chai7-cha2 chin-chiaN3 chhin-chhiuN7 oaN7 kut-thau5 lah; sim-lai7 teh kong2, ¡§Chin ki5-koai3! Goa2 e5 tiong7-hu chit-si5 an2-chaiN2-iuN7 e7 piN3 kau3 hiah-nih8 che7?¡¨ 
  Li2 sian-siN khoaN3 i-e5 bou2 sin-the2 siau-san2, in-chiuN5 phoa3-sam3, i-e5 kiaN2 thau5 ju5-ju5, kha chhiah-chhiah; chhu3-theh8 phoa3-sng2 teh-beh to2, ke-si mih8-kiaN7 khiam3-khoeh phaiN2-khoaN3. Hut-jian5 siong-sim bak8-sai2 lau5--chhut--lai5, chiu7 eng7 ho2 oe7, an-ui3 i-e5 bou2 kong2, ¡§Che long2-si7 goa2 e5 choe7-ko3, taN chhiaN2 li2 khoan-sim, chu7-kim i2-au7 oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3 in-tian2 pang-chan7, tek-khak beh chiau3-kou3 ke-lai7 bou2-kiaN2, m7-bian2 koh-chai3 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni-siN chiah-long5-poe7.¡¨ 
  Cho3 hoe2 tam5-lun7 tiap-a2-ku2, chiu7 khi3 khui siuN, chiong i sou2 hak e5 cha-bou2-lang5 in-chiuN5 theh8 hou7 in bou2; koh chiong saN, kap e5, hou7 i-e5 kiaN2 chheng7,soa3 hou7 i khi3 thi3-thau5 se2 seng-khu choan5-ke chit8-si5 cho3 chit8-e7 oaN7-sin. Kau3 teh-beh chiah8 png7, tai7-ke ui5-lui5 cho3-hoe2 che7, boe7 chiah8 e5 tai7-seng, Li2 sian-siN ki5-to2 Siong7-te3 kui2-ku3-oe7 chiah chiah8. In bou2 m7-bat ki5-to2 si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3 teh mng7 i. Li2 sian-siN ka7 i kong2,¡§Ki5-to2 si7 kiu5 Siong7-te3 si-in kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 su3-hok, kai3 iau3-kin2 e5 le2-sou3.¡¨ 
  Chit-si5 chhiaN2 ban7 kong2, kau3 e5-hng chiah ka7 li2 kong2 siong5-se3. TaN u7 chit8 ku3 iau3-kin2 e5 oe7 kap li2 su-niu5, cheng5 sou2 be7-khi3 hit nng7-e5 kiaN2, tek-khak tioh8 siok8-hoe5 to3--lai5; be7-khi3 m7-na7 siong-tioh8 pe7-kiaN2 e5 cheng5, koh hoan7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 hoat. 
  In bou2 thiaN che oe7, toa7 hoaN-hi2, sui-jian5 m7-bat hoan7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 hoat si7 sim2-mih8 oe7, chit-ku3 siong-tioh8 pe7-kiaN2 e5 cheng5 khiok e7-hiau2 thiaN. Tui3 hit nng7-e5 kiaN2 be7-khi3 liau2-au7 kau3 chit-tiap8 iau2-boe7 pang3-sim, chiu7 koaN2-kin2 in3 i-e5 tiong7-hu kong2,¡§Na7 siok8-hoe5 chit nng7-e5 kiaN2 goa2 e5 sim chiu7 an-jian5 lah.¡¨ 
  Li2 sian-siN kong2,¡§Goa2 bin5-a2-jit8 tek-khak beh chhin-sin khi3 tham3-thiaN, na7 chit nng7-e5 kiaN2 iau2 ti7-teh tek-khak beh siok8 to3--lai5. Chit8-ke toan5-toan5-iN5 chiu7-si7 khoai3-lok8 e5 su7.¡¨ 
  Chiah8 png7 liau2, khan i-e5 kiaN2 chhut-khi3 tham3 chhu3-piN peng5-iu2. Lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 toa7-toa7 teh ki5-koai3, long2 kong2,¡§Li2 sian-siN piN3-cho3 sin e5 lang5, chong2--si7 m7-chai i si7 tui3 tah8-loh8 piN3-cho3 kau3 an2-ni.¡¨ 
